\f2\b\fs24 \cf2 \strokec3 My honest recommendation:
\f1\b0 \'a0For a money management app with dashboards, trends, and aggregations \'97\'a0
\f2\b Azure SQL is the right choice
\f1\b0 , not Table Storage. Table Storage is ideal for logs, IoT telemetry, and simple key-value lookups \'97 not financial analytics.\
That said,\'a0
\f2\b if cost is the primary concern
\f1\b0 , a hybrid works: Azure Table Storage for raw expense logs + a lightweight Azure SQL for dashboard aggregations.\
