Sugati exists as a word in Sanskrit and Pali traditions meaning auspicious journey or good path. It appears in Buddhist texts. There are some small businesses and NGOs in India using it as a name. But whether any of them have a registered trademark in your specific category I genuinely cannot confirm reliably.\
